\description{
An \link[R6:R6Class]{R6} class that configures tree hybridizing operations in
\pkg{nitro}.

Tree hybridizing generates new candidate trees by combining subtrees from
different source trees, selecting the best results, and optionally
replacing the source trees. This wraps the TNT \code{tfuse} command with the
\code{hybrid} subcommand.
}
